could not outshine the gray.</i>

03:47.102 --> 03:49.852
<i>When her best friend, Jessie, lost her mom,</i>

03:51.147 --> 03:55.987
<i>she realized not every story has
a happy ending.</i>

03:58.154 --> 04:02.624
<i>So the girl grew up
and left fairy tales behind,</i>

04:03.993 --> 04:07.583
