there's a thing on addiction and stuff.

21:29.164 --> 21:30.874
Wow. What a coincidence.

21:30.915 --> 21:34.035
The way I see it, you kind of owe me one.
All right?

21:34.085 --> 21:36.705
So just think about going in there

21:36.796 --> 21:40.126
and listening to an ex-drug addict
who happens to be my manager.

21:40.216 --> 21:41.296
He's your boss.

21:41.509 --> 21:44.009
