21:48.099 --> 21:51.059
He was a crack whore.
You're calling me a crack whore then?

21:51.144 --> 21:52.194
No, you're not a crack... It's the first...

21:52.228 --> 21:54.438
It's the only drug slang thing I know.
I don't...

21:54.522 --> 21:56.022
