been off your medication?

28:09.022 --> 28:10.402
Are you gonna let me in or no?

28:10.565 --> 28:12.065
Is my audition finished?

28:12.108 --> 28:14.528
You need a dance
or a little song or something?

28:14.694 --> 28:17.824
No, but I do need to see your arm.

28:19.074 --> 28:20.834
Congratulations, guys.

28:20.909 --> 28:24.999
